@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}
<style>
    .box {
    background-color:aliceblue;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    }

    .box h2, .box h3 {
    color: #666;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 0;
    }

    .box p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    }

    .box li {
    padding: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    .box li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    }

    .box strong {
    color: #3498db;
    font-weight: bold;
    }
    .h3{
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color:black; 
    margin-top: 20px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
</style>

    <div class="container-fluid mt-4">
        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid text-center">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to SahasBank</h1>
                <p class="lead">Your trusted partner in financial services.</p>
                <hr class="my-4">
                <p>Explore our services and manage your finances with ease.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="MainPage" role="button">Learn more</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5em; color:black; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            About Us
        </h2>

        <div class="box">
            <p>Welcome to <strong>Sahas Bank</strong>, where we believe in creating a brighter financial future for everyone. Established in 2005, Sahas Bank has grown to become a trusted name in the banking industry, known for our commitment to innovation, customer service, and community involvement.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>At Sahas Bank, our mission is to provide exceptional financial services that empower our customers to achieve their financial goals. We strive to offer innovative solutions, personalized service, and a seamless banking experience.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>We envision a world where everyone has access to the financial tools and resources they need to succeed. Our goal is to be at the forefront of banking technology, continuously evolving to meet the changing needs of our customers.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Our Values</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Integrity</strong>: We uphold the highest standards of integrity in all our actions.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Focus</strong>: Our customers are at the heart of everything we do.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation</strong>: We embrace change and continuously seek new ways to improve.</li>
                <li><strong>Community</strong>: We are committed to making a positive impact in the communities we serve.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h3>Our History</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>Sahas Bank was founded by a group of visionary entrepreneurs who saw the need for a bank that truly understands and serves its customers. Over the years, we have expanded our services and grown our customer base, but our core values have remained the same.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Our Services</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>We offer a wide range of financial services, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Banking</strong>: Checking and savings accounts, personal loans, credit cards, and more.</li>
                <li><strong>Business Banking</strong>: Business accounts, loans, merchant services, and financial planning.</li>
                <li><strong>Investment Services</strong>: Wealth management, retirement planning, and investment advice.</li>
                <li><strong>Digital Banking</strong>: Online and mobile banking, digital wallets, and 24/7 customer support.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h3>Meet Our Team</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>Our team is made up of dedicated professionals who are passionate about helping our customers succeed. From our customer service representatives to our financial advisors, every member of the Sahas Bank team is here to support you.</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <div class="box">
            <p>We are here to help! If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
            <p><strong>Email</strong>: support@sahasbank.com</p>
            <p><strong>Phone</strong>: +962355651</p>

        </div>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Sahas Bank. We look forward to serving you and helping you achieve your financial dreams.</p>
    </div>



